<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reach-n">reach <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /riːtʃ/    美 /riːtʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1u">1.<strong>[U] (手、力量、影响的) 范围：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The shelf is so high that it is well <strong>out of / beyond my reach</strong>. 
架子太高，我根本够不到。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The new mobile phone is priced well <strong>within the reach of</strong> most people. 
那款新手机的定价在大多数人承受的范围内。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The beach is <strong>within easy reach of</strong> (= close to) the hotel.
酒店离海滩很近。</p></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] [常用复数] 河段；水域：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the upper reaches of the Nile 
尼罗河上游</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— I’m looking for a nearby place for my holiday. Any good ideas?
— How about the Moon Lake? It is <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ easy reach of the city.  （2013 上海改）  </li>
<li>Always remember to put such dangerous things as knives <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ children’s reach.  （2011 四川改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. within  2. out of / beyond  </p></div>